  "description": "SPI host controller supporting Standard, Dual, and Quad SPI modes with configurable chip select lines, TX/RX FIFOs, command queue, and 16-bit clock divider. TileLink-UL slave interface with passthrough mode for flash access. Extracted from OpenTitan (lowRISC).",
